assets upon the sale of such assets to provide you with the potential for future liquidity through the sale of our assets a sale or merger of our company or a listing of our common shares on a national securities exchange in order to meet our investment objectives we employ a dual strategy intended to generate current cash flow and capital appreciation there is no assurance that these investment objectives will be met our dual strategy when you invest with first capital real estate trust incorporated you join those investors who expect to benefit from our dual strategy we focus on acquiring existing stabilized cashflowing assets to support stable consistent distributions to our shareholders and we focus on acquiring opportunistic assets which we can reposition redevelop or remarket to create valueenhancement and capital appreciation by pursuing both strategies simultaneously we believe we can most effectively achieve our desired investment objectives prospectus risk considerations the material contained by this website may not be copied or reprinted in any way without written permission from first capital real estate trust incorporated   broad street new york phone     email copyright  first capital real estate trust incorporated home contact us privacy legal disclaimer risk considerations prospectus first capital real estate trust incorporated  materials due diligence login shareholder login materials and forms homefilings and formsmaterials and forms prospectus and supplements sec filings xbrl exhibits corporate governance materials and forms forms download     form    download     form    download     subscription agreement download     additional subscription agreement prospectus risk considerations the material contained by this website may not be copied or reprinted in any way without written permission from first capital real estate trust incorporated   broad street new york phone     email copyright  first capital real estate trust incorporated home contact 